snippet.title: SYNERGY - Early Access OUT NOW | One of the most highly anticipated City Builders of 2024 on Steam!
snippet.description:
The Early Access is now available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1989070/Synergy?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=ea_outnow

Synergy is a city-building game in which humanity must survive in a strange and hostile world. Build a city while respecting the ecosystem. Explore and analyze your environment. Provide for the needs of your citizens.

Inspired by great games like Pharaoh or Frostpunk
